Package address.data

Class AddressEntry

java.lang.Object
address.data.AddressEntry
public class AddressEntry
extends java.lang.Object
The AddressEntry class represents an entry in an address book. contains variables firstName, lastName, street, city, state, zip, telephone, email for storing address details
Since:
Feb. 26, 2024
